Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.00,0:00:12.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,掌上的微風
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.94,0:00:20.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在光芒中一閃一閃地舞動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:20.61,0:00:26.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已經能用全新的笑容
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:26.55,0:00:34.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,向陌生人道早安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:34.29,0:00:40.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,儘管回憶溢滿心頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:41.03,0:00:46.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的朝氣絕不認輸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:46.84,0:00:51.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無所謂在乾掉的淚痕中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:51.24,0:00:56.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有一扇通往夢想的門
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:56.28,0:01:00.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果煩惱就無法前進
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:00.52,0:01:01.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:01.85,0:01:09.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會以迎接朋友的方式\N溫柔地微笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:09.32,0:01:13.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是我們的約定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:14.00,0:01:18.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無意間悲傷雖然湧上心頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:18.43,0:01:22.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也會試著與人和好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:22.97,0:01:27.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為這是我們的約定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:40.56,0:01:44.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,討厭,不要咬啦\N我要生氣囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:44.73,0:01:46.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走開啦\N惣一郎,過來這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.43,0:01:51.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代什麼時候才會回來啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.53,0:01:53.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代?不知道耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.97,0:01:56.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管理員說他明天就會回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.04,0:02:00.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明天啊,真無聊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.21,0:02:01.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.71,0:02:08.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得太安靜了\N安靜到快讓人抓狂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.45,0:02:13.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊,回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.29,0:02:18.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我過完年回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.86,0:02:20.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,四谷,你回來啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.23,0:02:22.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說曹操曹操就到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.90,0:02:25.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今年也請多多關照
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.47,0:02:26.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好,請多關照
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.40,0:02:29.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來,喝酒喝酒,快來陪我喝酒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.54,0:02:30.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有帶任何禮物喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.94,0:02:32.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.61,0:02:36.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他是從哪裡回來的啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.61,0:02:40.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,傳過來,交給我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.32,0:02:41.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,學長,進攻進攻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.89,0:02:45.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,傳給我,傳給我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.36,0:02:50.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,響子,妳知道嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.39,0:02:54.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別看我弱不禁風的樣子\N其實我高中打過橄欖球喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.86,0:02:55.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加油!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.86,0:02:57.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代加油!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.93,0:02:59.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,達陣!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.34,0:03:04.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,響子,請看我的神勇英姿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.29,0:03:27.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,#20響子焦慮不安?\N五代遲遲未歸之謎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.64,0:03:40.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂,哎呀,五代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.01,0:03:44.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還要兩三天嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.38,0:03:49.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的,我決定延個幾天回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.29,0:03:53.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為我爸媽捨不得我離開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.46,0:03:58.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了\N你就好好地陪陪爸媽吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.30,0:04:03.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼爸媽捨不得你走?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.13,0:04:05.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這種事怎麼可以說實話呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.37,0:04:08.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哼,死要面子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.17,0:04:08.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,囉嗦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.14,0:04:16.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個樣子\N怎麼可以讓管理員看到呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.16,0:04:32.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有空嗎?\N有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.13,0:04:33.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以進來一下嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.76,0:04:35.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以啊,請進
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.81,0:04:50.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼事嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.21,0:04:53.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽說五代今天會回來啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.58,0:04:57.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他剛才打電話來\N說還要在那裡待兩三天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.45,0:05:00.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來,請喝茶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.19,0:05:06.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好寂寞喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.37,0:05:15.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽說除夕夜\N只有你們兩個獨處?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.01,0:05:19.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事都沒發生喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.17,0:05:22.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳這麼說,話題就接不下去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.31,0:05:22.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.01,0:05:24.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,連手都沒有牽?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.45,0:05:27.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對啊,那是個平靜到\N令人驚訝的夜晚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.82,0:05:32.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了,要是出事的話\N我有一半的責任
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.09,0:05:35.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳想太多了啦\N這是可喜可賀的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.09,0:05:36.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這話什麼意思?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.03,0:05:39.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過他為什麼要延後回來呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.73,0:05:42.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可能是想家吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.77,0:05:46.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼啦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.97,0:05:48.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比起心愛的女人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.44,0:05:49.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他還是喜歡他老媽嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.04,0:05:51.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.24,0:05:53.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎麼說\N畢竟他還只是個孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.81,0:05:56.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這也是他的一片孝心啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.14,0:05:58.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去年暑假他也沒有回去啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.85,0:06:00.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.58,0:06:05.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比起去年,他的確成熟多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.55,0:06:07.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,尤其是身體方面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.76,0:06:09.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟已經二十歲了嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.73,0:06:12.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對啊對啊,已經是個男人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.76,0:06:18.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的什麼都沒發生啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.43,0:06:19.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們很不死心耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.04,0:06:22.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,連接吻都沒有嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.44,0:06:25.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.56,0:06:51.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其實我喜歡的是五代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.60,0:06:54.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,音無小姐,怎麼這樣!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.30,0:06:59.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是,一旦分隔兩地\N我就快被寂寞擊垮了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.51,0:07:01.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,儘量被寂寞擊垮吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.99,0:07:11.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好,就這麼做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.12,0:07:21.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管…管理員!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.07,0:07:31.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奶奶,妳幹嘛?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.48,0:07:36.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你夢到管理員啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.01,0:07:39.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才沒有呢,我才沒有夢到她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.02,0:07:43.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管…管理員!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.19,0:07:44.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要這樣啦!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.23,0:07:52.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,裕作,你什麼時候回東京?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.96,0:07:54.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道,瘀青成這樣的話…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.03,0:07:58.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看你乾脆在這裡\N待到初十五吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.80,0:08:00.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦?為什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.50,0:08:03.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在這裡過完成人式再回去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.47,0:08:07.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別開玩笑了,如果我待這麼久\N那場夢就會成真了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.61,0:08:10.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管…管理員!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.15,0:08:12.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奶奶,不要鬧了啦!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.56,0:08:21.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,音無小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.46,0:08:26.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下一起去喝杯咖啡如何?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.03,0:08:32.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天是初九\N五代說不定會回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.17,0:08:34.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳就去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.74,0:08:38.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,趁這個時候\N讓教練安慰妳一下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.74,0:08:40.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳怎麼這麼說呢!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.11,0:08:41.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這話什麼意思?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.71,0:08:46.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代遲遲不回來\N這個人好像覺得很寂寞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.08,0:08:46.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.85,0:08:48.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳又在胡說八道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.59,0:08:53.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼,我們去喝杯咖啡吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.59,0:08:57.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,該不會把我當成五代的代打吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.76,0:09:00.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,討厭,怎麼連你都這麼說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.63,0:09:03.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鄉下啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.27,0:09:08.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真羨慕老家在鄉下的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.20,0:09:10.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀,你是東京人嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.87,0:09:13.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對啊,妳呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.48,0:09:17.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為我爸工作的關係\N我經常轉學
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.38,0:09:20.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以對老家沒什麼特別的感情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.32,0:09:29.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們說妳很寂寞\N這是真的嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.93,0:09:32.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為五代遲遲不回來嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.23,0:09:37.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,討厭,請你不要當真啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.27,0:09:39.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,實在太扯了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.47,0:09:42.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.92,0:10:03.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.60,0:10:11.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛,還沒回來啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.81,0:10:21.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳回來啦,這麼早就回來啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.94,0:10:24.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是五代回來\N沒有出來迎接他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.11,0:10:24.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣他太可憐了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.01,0:10:27.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比起教練,妳還是選擇五代啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.58,0:10:29.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是身為管理員的義務
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.35,0:10:31.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,義務是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.39,0:10:35.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過,他要回來的話\N應該會先連絡一下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.03,0:10:40.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說得也是喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.33,0:10:41.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳很在意嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.66,0:10:43.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為我是管理員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.77,0:10:53.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝光臨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.02,0:11:05.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我復活了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.39,0:11:09.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題,這樣就能見人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.59,0:11:11.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快打電話給管理員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.26,0:11:14.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂!裕作!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.36,0:11:18.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你每天都在家裡打混\N還不給我到店裡幫忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.27,0:11:20.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是,我現在…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.77,0:11:24.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,少囉嗦,快點出去外送
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.04,0:11:30.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡,就會使喚我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.18,0:11:33.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且還挑我想打電話\N給管理員的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.38,0:11:37.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管理員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.95,0:11:39.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明天就能見面了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.23,0:11:46.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,響子,我回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.26,0:11:48.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓妳等了這麼久
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.20,0:11:51.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代,我好寂寞喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.83,0:11:54.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是我沒有被寂寞打敗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.50,0:11:55.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,響子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.94,0:12:00.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,響子!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.84,0:12:05.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.79,0:12:50.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我出去一下囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.46,0:12:51.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好,路上小心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.99,0:12:53.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,千萬不要喝太多喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.43,0:12:54.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.41,0:13:09.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你明天打算怎麼辦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.44,0:13:10.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會回去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.12,0:13:17.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幹嘛笑得這麼誇張
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.89,0:13:19.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為你那張臉…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.22,0:13:23.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不准笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.73,0:13:29.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,笑死人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.73,0:13:31.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.73,0:13:35.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,結果你明天到底…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.20,0:13:38.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這張臉怎麼回去呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.21,0:13:40.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管…管理員!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.66,0:13:59.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們是怎麼了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.49,0:14:01.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得好無聊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.93,0:14:05.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們可以像平常一樣\N在樓上喝酒狂歡啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.40,0:14:08.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是,總是提不起勁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.37,0:14:13.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大概是因為缺少了\N五代這個配角吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.82,0:14:24.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂,哪位?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.02,0:14:28.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代\N你什麼時候要回來呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.36,0:14:31.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦?還要兩三天?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.59,0:14:34.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不,可能要三四天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.90,0:14:37.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會儘早回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.63,0:14:39.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過還無法確定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.73,0:14:41.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼久嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.60,0:14:45.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代,是不是出了什麼事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.61,0:14:47.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有啦,沒什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.61,0:14:51.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是被我爸媽攔著…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.61,0:14:55.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有人攔著你喔!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.40,0:15:11.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管理員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.60,0:15:16.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管理員,我在叫妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.01,0:15:18.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀,小津江
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.28,0:15:22.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳怎麼啦?怎麼一直在發呆?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.81,0:15:24.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有,沒什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.61,0:15:26.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出來買東西嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.58,0:15:27.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.78,0:15:31.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,倒是五代究竟是怎麼了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.15,0:15:33.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,居然說還要待在鄉下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.55,0:15:37.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真過份\N我們約好10號要去看電影的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.83,0:15:40.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳也不知道原因嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.16,0:15:44.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對啊,昨晚他有打電話來\N說他爸媽硬是留他下來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.63,0:15:46.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說得不清不楚的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.04,0:15:49.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.48,0:15:56.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好寂寞喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.83,0:16:19.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.67,0:16:20.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你回來啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.57,0:16:21.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙回來了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.74,0:16:25.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誰?沒有,還沒回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.24,0:16:26.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無聊透了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.54,0:16:30.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙到底在搞什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.83,0:16:47.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好冷喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.98,0:17:02.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已經是11號了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.71,0:17:05.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他到底在做什麼呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.61,0:17:39.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來是風啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.66,0:18:59.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幹嘛啦!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.19,0:19:01.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要這樣啦!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.93,0:19:03.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,住手!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.03,0:19:06.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,每天窩在家裡打混\N你這個礙事鬼!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.87,0:19:08.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快給我回東京去!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.64,0:19:12.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳不是叫我待到成人式嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.27,0:19:14.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我以為你會在店裡幫點忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.81,0:19:19.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是你看看你\N一個大男生居然成天在照鏡子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.41,0:19:22.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不是垃圾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.18,0:19:23.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,裕作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.35,0:19:27.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看你這個樣子\N書大概也唸得不怎麼樣吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.76,0:19:31.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,乾脆回來娶個老婆\N繼承這家店吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.69,0:19:35.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會變成這樣\N我才不要呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.66,0:19:37.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就快點滾回去!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.33,0:19:40.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也很想啊,可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.91,0:19:56.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代真的好慢喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.35,0:19:59.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,學校都已經開學了,不是嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.95,0:20:01.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都已經是14號了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.79,0:20:03.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可能是想家吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.76,0:20:06.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎麼說\N他畢竟還是個孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.50,0:20:10.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他暑假也沒有回去啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.63,0:20:13.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳不是說,這是他的一片孝心嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.33,0:20:16.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎?我有說過這種話嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.57,0:20:23.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是傷腦筋\N這個月的房租都還沒有交呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.41,0:20:25.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們聽到了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.51,0:20:28.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,房租晚個十天交也無所謂吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.55,0:20:30.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看來她真的發飆了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.75,0:20:33.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這種時候最好不要捉弄她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.92,0:20:36.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,悄悄話請不要講得這麼大聲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.66,0:20:39.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管理員,微笑\N要隨時保持微笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.53,0:20:45.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人生有苦有樂\N男人不只有五代一個人而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.40,0:20:47.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你說這是什麼話?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.20,0:20:49.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像我喜歡五代似的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.27,0:20:53.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為妳看起來真的很沮喪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.24,0:20:57.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我才沒有沮喪呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.11,0:21:00.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只是身為管理員的責任…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:01.38,0:21:03.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會不會是五代回來了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.85,0:21:05.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是風的聲音吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:05.92,0:21:07.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我去看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:07.39,0:21:08.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走吧,走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:11.56,0:21:12.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼?妳不去看嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.03,0:21:15.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果回來了\N他會出聲說“我回來了”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:15.50,0:21:17.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳還真愛賭氣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.37,0:21:23.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:24.07,0:21:25.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代,你回來啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.54,0:21:28.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼到現在才回來啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:28.18,0:21:30.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為發生了一點事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:31.01,0:21:32.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:37.25,0:21:40.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管理員,快來看快來看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:40.99,0:21:44.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用了啦\N我想把行李放回房間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:44.33,0:21:47.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼啊\N你們很久沒有見面了,不是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:47.40,0:21:50.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用了啦\N我又沒有特別想見她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:50.90,0:21:52.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他說什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:53.87,0:21:57.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管理員,妳聽到了嗎?\N快啊,快來看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:01.51,0:22:02.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我現在沒空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:03.58,0:22:06.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別管那個了\N總之快點過來啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:06.41,0:22:07.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底有什麼事嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:07.58,0:22:09.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代,不要這樣嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:09.32,0:22:10.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不要去見她啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:10.35,0:22:11.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:16.26,0:22:17.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:18.09,0:22:21.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛,居然戴著墨鏡裝帥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:21.70,0:22:23.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼,讓各位久等了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:23.33,0:22:24.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謎底揭曉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:24.47,0:22:26.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋,不要這樣啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:26.63,0:22:28.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,住手,不要這樣啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:30.14,0:22:32.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊,巨人在哭泣著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:49.36,0:22:53.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然應該在鄉下老家\N多待個兩三天才對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:53.59,0:22:55.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代回來了真好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:56.06,0:22:58.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好久沒有看到管理員的笑容了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:58.33,0:23:00.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這種也叫笑容嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:05.01,0:23:06.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總之來喝兩杯吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:06.31,0:23:08.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好久沒喝了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:23.06,0:23:24.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:25.46,0:23:27.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:50.78,0:23:53.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最近五代變得很奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:53.35,0:23:56.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鬼鬼祟祟地\N好像在避著我似的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:56.09,0:23:57.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定有問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:57.86,0:24:01.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,相聚一刻下一回\N「五代危機!一刻館的小貓物語!」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:02.00,0:24:04.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀,居然把貓取成我的名字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:04.36,0:24:07.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,響子響子的\N請不要叫得這麼親熱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:27.52,0:24:35.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那天在陌生的城市下了一場陣雨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:35.46,0:24:42.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳非常在意淋溼的高跟鞋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:42.40,0:24:50.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從前妳用那隱藏著\N稚氣的側臉和我交談
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:50.38,0:24:56.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳說的話語至今仍能想起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:56.55,0:25:03.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一開始就彷佛\N置身電影中的感覺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:04.36,0:25:11.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳輕聲細語地說著\N安靜的最後一幕
